- 2026-05-07: Madurai Srirangam Iyengar (bridge era, Sangeet Natak Akademi awardee) was R. Vedavalli's first guru — lineage sourced from the SNA award PDF. SNA award PDFs (source-type: pdf) are an accepted source for musicians without Wikipedia pages.
- 2026-05-07: For standalone alapana clips (no full concert context), attach directly to the primary musician's youtube[] array with label "Alapana", raga_id set, composition_id omitted — no recording file needed. First artist in the description is the primary; others are added as performers via --performer or add-youtube-performer.
