- 2026-05-09: The ni_nama_rupamulaku / ni_nama_roopamulaku duplicate was discovered; both IDs existed with live references across different recordings — always grep recordings/ for both variants before collapsing; keep the more complete/more-referenced file as canonical.
- 2026-05-09: neevaada_ne_gaana (Saranga/Tyagaraja, c2671) already existed — running composition-exists by playlist title ("Nivadane Gana") missed it; always also grep the compositions directory with ls | grep <partial> and check the Karnatik URL before adding a new composition file.
- 2026-05-09: Bowli is a janya of Mayamalavagowla (mela 15), not Natabhairavi — always verify parent raga against Wikipedia before adding; the tracklist spelling "baulī" is an alias, not the canonical raga name; Kokiladhvani (janya of Harikambhoji/mela 28) has no Wikipedia article — drmradhakrishnan.com is an accepted specialist source for rare janyas.
